35
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,690
between us?

36
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,100
Is that what you think?

37
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:50,820
I thought you'd be happy for me.

38
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,540
I am.

39
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:56,130
You always said

40
00:01:57,310 --> 00:01:58,460
I should

41
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,620
make my own way

42
00:02:00,350 --> 00:02:01,290
and earn a living on my own.

43
00:02:02,510 --> 00:02:04,330
I'm heading that way now.

44
00:02:07,710 --> 00:02:08,780
That's true.

45
00:02:09,470 --> 00:02:10,100
Shaohua.

46
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:13,690
I used to depend on you.

47
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:17,220
But now I can challenge you.

48
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,410
Isn't that a good thing?

49
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:26,890
Erniu, I'm sorry.

50
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,220
I was being narrow-minded about you.

51
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,380
While seeing you do this

52
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,450
hurts a little,

53
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:36,100
I'm so proud

54
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,410
to see how far you've come.

55
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,570
That's great.

56
00:02:44,590 --> 00:02:45,610
But seriously,

57
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,170
I'm really happy.

58
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,220
I used to not get

59
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,890
why you all had that gleam in your eyes

60
00:02:54,470 --> 00:02:56,100
whenever you talked about business.

61
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,730
Now that I'm part of it, I finally get

62
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,100
why you were all so excited.

63
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:02,100
And honestly, it's a blast.

64
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,730
Nothing else

65
00:03:03,910 --> 00:03:05,500
even comes close to that feeling.

66
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:06,540
You're right.

67
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,570
And let me warn you.

68
00:03:10,030 --> 00:03:11,850
I admit I underestimated you before,

69
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:14,220
and that's why you caught me off guard.

70
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:15,850
But from now on,

71
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,940
I'm going to go all out.

72
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,820
Bring it on.

73
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,450
The best way to respect a rival

74
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,940
is to give it your all.

75
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:29,450
And

76
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,380
let's get one thing straight.

77
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,100
No matter how this battle ends,

78
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,820
we can't let it come between us.

79
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:37,690
Of course.

80
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:39,690
Business is one thing.

81
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,010
Personal feelings are another.

82
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,410
Why don't we have newspaper carriers

83
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:50,220
slip an ad flier

84
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,820
into every newspaper they sell?

85
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,660
We can pay them

86
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,980
one wen a piece.

87
00:03:55,430 --> 00:03:57,730
It's a win-win. They make more money

88
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,980
and we get a huge boost
in brand awareness for the Miracle Pill.

89
00:04:01,710 --> 00:04:03,610
It costs less than placing ads
the usual way.

90
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,220
And it works better.

91
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,660
Should we adjust
the TCM apothecaries' rebates

92
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,290
and payment terms
to match the Yushu Pill's?

93
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:12,060
Rather than letting the profits
go to TCM apothecaries,

94
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,820
why not let our customers
benefit instead?

95
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:15,290
How?

96
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,250
Regulars of Miracle Pill

97
00:04:17,480 --> 00:04:18,490
can get 10% off

98
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:21,340
with one empty bottle
when they repurchase.

99
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,930
Two bottles

100
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:23,610
mean 20% off,

101
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:24,540
and so on.

102
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,140
With ten empty bottles,

103
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,580
they get a free one.

104
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:29,660
Additionally,

105
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,730
regulars

106
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,900
who bring in new customers

107
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,780
get

108
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,290
a free bottle, too.

109
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,730
This way,

110
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,930
we retain existing customers

111
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:40,900
while attracting new ones.

112
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,250
I've crunched the numbers.

113
00:04:42,510 --> 00:04:43,810
If 100 bottles are sold,

114
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:45,490
TCM apothecaries

115
00:04:45,950 --> 00:04:47,290
earn more from Yushu Pill

116
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,930
than from Miracle Pill.

117
00:04:49,190 --> 00:04:51,580
But when they sell 1,000 bottles,

118
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,700
Miracle Pill

119
00:04:52,720 --> 00:04:53,900
earns them five times

120
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,250
more than Yushu Pill.

121
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:58,460
So even generous rebates
and payment terms

122
00:04:58,500 --> 00:05:00,660
can't match the appeal
of fast-growing sales

123
00:05:00,940 --> 00:05:02,700
to the owners.

124
00:05:05,300 --> 00:05:07,140
It's a solid approach,

125
00:05:07,140 --> 00:05:08,500
but easy to replicate.

126
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:09,900
I'd say

127
00:05:09,900 --> 00:05:10,820
within a month,

128
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:11,940
Jujing Apothecary will follow suit.

129
00:05:12,460 --> 00:05:13,340
It doesn't matter.

130
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:16,940
This strategy only works if the medicine

131
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:17,980
is truly effective.

132
00:05:18,420 --> 00:05:20,220
Even if Jujing Apothecary
tries the same thing,

133
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:21,900
it won't work for them

134
00:05:22,020 --> 00:05:23,420
without real results

135
00:05:23,660 --> 00:05:24,700
from the Yushu Pill.

136
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,420
I have always been confident

137
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,500
in the efficacy of Miracle Pill.

138
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:30,220
Right.

139
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:32,380
The real battle starts now.

140
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:36,260
Miss Bai has signed exclusive agreements

141
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:38,860
with over 80 TCM apothecaries.

142
