However,

143
00:05:40,340 --> 00:05:42,540
more than 300 others

144
00:05:42,540 --> 00:05:43,620
are open to us.

145
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:45,300
That's why the next week

146
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,340
is so critical.

147
00:05:46,540 --> 00:05:48,980
We have to visit all of these

148
00:05:50,780 --> 00:05:52,940
to distribute samples,
explain the efficacy,

149
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,700
and introduce our policies.

150
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:56,860
We'll divide everyone in the company

151
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:57,940
into teams of two,

152
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,020
with each team assigned
to a specific region.

153
