but the bigger picture
is still uncertain.

162
00:06:18,780 --> 00:06:20,260
With a market as big as Shanghai's,

163
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:23,460
there's plenty of room

164
00:06:23,580 --> 00:06:24,660
for both Yushu and Miracle Pills.

165
00:06:25,060 --> 00:06:26,900
Absolutely not.

166
00:06:27,460 --> 00:06:28,780
If Miracle Pill stays ahead,

167
00:06:28,940 --> 00:06:30,780
everything I've planned falls apart.

168
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:31,820
What plan?

169
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:35,980
We've got one month

170
00:06:36,980 --> 00:06:38,420
to take Miracle Pill out of the game.

171
00:06:39,460 --> 00:06:40,900
This upcoming month

172
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:42,060
is crucial.

173
00:06:42,380 --> 00:06:44,500
Unless we push back
against Jujing's aggressive campaign,

174
00:06:44,700 --> 00:06:45,820
