178
00:06:51,620 --> 00:06:54,580
dealing with Chu Shaohua
will be a whole lot easier.

179
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:55,900
Now

180
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,460
we can't beat

181
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:59,340
Jujing Apothecary on our own.

182
00:07:00,180 --> 00:07:02,100
We need to seek new partners.

183
00:07:03,740 --> 00:07:05,020
