out of the TCM business.

188
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:15,060
He kept one main store,

189
00:07:15,060 --> 00:07:16,940
but all the other branches
were converted into trade houses.

190
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:20,260
They're mainly selling fabrics,
medical equipment,

191
00:07:20,260 --> 00:07:21,420
salt, kerosene,

192
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:22,580
and other local specialties now.

193
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,860
