218
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:33,900
One is you.

219
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:36,220
And the other is you.

220
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,620
You're

221
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:40,540
just a low-born wannabe,

222
00:08:40,860 --> 00:08:42,820
scrambling for a seat at a table
you'll never belong to.

223
00:08:43,380 --> 00:08:43,940
And you're

224
