nothing but a devious plotter,

225
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:48,260
always scheming behind my back.

226
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:50,140
With the two of you?

227
00:08:50,500 --> 00:08:51,300
Let's be honest.

228
00:08:51,300 --> 00:08:52,420
Working with you?

229
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:53,460
Not a chance.

230
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:58,180
Tongdao, why let money
slip through your fingers?

231
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,220
Exactly.

232
00:08:59,300 --> 00:09:00,540
