233
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,820
And businessmen don't say no to money.

234
00:09:02,980 --> 00:09:05,460
So now I'm giving both of you a chance.

235
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:06,260
Start flattering me.

236
00:09:07,020 --> 00:09:08,460
I'll cooperate

237
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:10,020
with whoever makes me happy.

238
00:09:11,740 --> 00:09:13,380
Come on, butter me up.

239
00:09:18,020 --> 00:09:18,780
Tongdao,

240
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:20,860
please take a look at this.

241
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:23,020
The prices,

242
00:09:23,340 --> 00:09:25,140
payment terms, and rebates

243
00:09:25,540 --> 00:09:26,620
are all in here.

244
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:29,100
It's an incredibly generous deal.

245
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:30,460
Just read it.

246
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:31,980
I promise you'll like it.

247
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:42,540
Your turn.

248
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:45,780
Flatter me.

249
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:50,660
Why would I do that?

250
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:53,380
