254
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:01,900
and bring back

255
00:10:01,900 --> 00:10:02,940
your former glory.

256
00:10:03,700 --> 00:10:04,900
But sorry,

257
00:10:05,260 --> 00:10:06,420
we

258
