don't do rebates,

259
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:09,260
price cuts,

260
00:10:09,860 --> 00:10:11,580
or payment plans.

261
00:10:12,540 --> 00:10:13,940
What we do offer

262
00:10:14,580 --> 00:10:15,660
is a win-win partnership.

263
00:10:38,580 --> 00:10:39,260
Tongdao,

264
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:43,220
all the terms I mentioned

265
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:45,220
are negotiable.

266
00:10:50,780 --> 00:10:52,420
Miss Chu

267
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:57,660
already gave me
a cut of Miracle Pill's profits.

268
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:03,540
We can do the same.

269
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:06,700
Miss Chu gave a full 10%.

270
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:07,820
We'll give 15%.

271
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,420
That's tempting.

272
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:16,620
Mr. Tian,

273
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:18,740
I don't think you want to make a deal.

274
00:11:19,260 --> 00:11:20,020
You just want to sit back

275
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:22,060
and watch Miss Bai and me go at it.

276
00:11:25,420 --> 00:11:26,540
You got it right.

277
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,660
Back then,

278
00:11:30,300 --> 00:11:33,300
