279
00:11:33,980 --> 00:11:34,780
just to embarrass me,

280
00:11:34,780 --> 00:11:37,380
well, maybe just a little.

281
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:38,860
But still,

282
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:41,580
watching you two claw at each other now,

283
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:43,380
I've got to say I'm loving it.

284
00:11:47,780 --> 00:11:48,300
Shaohua.

285
00:11:48,300 --> 00:11:49,260
What are you doing?

