00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:56,660
I'm looking for Wen Zhiqiu.

573
00:25:57,260 --> 00:25:58,300
Where is he?

574
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:12,940
Running an apothecary is tough.

575
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,780
Doing trade is way easier,

576
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:15,580
right?

577
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:17,500
If you have...

578
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:18,260
Zhiqiu.

579
00:26:25,140 --> 00:26:25,820
She's

580
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:29,500
my former fiancée,

581
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:31,660
Miss Chu Shaohua.

582
00:26:35,100 --> 00:26:35,660
I...

583
00:26:36,580 --> 00:26:38,780
Didn't you say you were done with me?

584
00:26:39,380 --> 00:26:40,260
Why the sudden visit?

585
00:26:40,820 --> 00:26:41,740
Is something bothering you?

586
00:26:42,820 --> 00:26:43,500
No.

587
00:26:44,180 --> 00:26:45,100
- I...
- Then,

588
00:26:46,460 --> 00:26:47,140
missing me, huh?

589
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,340
I'm not sure I can handle that.

590
00:26:50,220 --> 00:26:51,660
If people start talking,

591
00:26:52,140 --> 00:26:53,740
my whole reputation

592
00:26:54,060 --> 00:26:55,260
is toast.

593
00:26:58,660 --> 00:27:00,260
Do you really think
you have a good reputation?

594
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:02,380
Since we parted ways,

595
00:27:03,340 --> 00:27:05,140
your foes have become my friends.

596
00:27:06,060 --> 00:27:07,140
Things have really opened up for me.

597
00:27:07,620 --> 00:27:08,460
Feels like I can breathe again.

598
00:27:08,940 --> 00:27:10,620
Everything just flows now.

599
00:27:12,780 --> 00:27:13,460
Miss Chu,

600
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:15,260
please

601
00:27:16,180 --> 00:27:16,820
go back.

602
00:27:16,820 --> 00:27:18,660
♪Even good medicine can't heal the soul♪

603
00:27:19,100 --> 00:27:24,380
♪The machinations of my conscience
drive me into perdition♪

604
00:27:24,380 --> 00:27:25,140
Are you sure

605
00:27:26,100 --> 00:27:28,020
you know why I came to you?

606
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:32,380
♪Let my breath run ragged, run ragged♪

607
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:34,540
After all these years,

608
00:27:34,700 --> 00:27:36,820
♪Lost in love,
how could I ever fool myself again?♪

609
00:27:36,820 --> 00:27:38,700
of course I know you inside and out.

610
00:27:40,660 --> 00:27:45,580
♪When you and I bloom
into an entwined mystery♪

611
00:27:45,580 --> 00:27:46,220
Yes.

612
00:27:46,940 --> 00:27:49,380
♪As we walk toward the same thorns♪

613
00:27:49,380 --> 00:27:50,780
I've known you for over ten years.

614
00:27:53,220 --> 00:27:54,860
You really had me completely fooled.

615
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:56,900
♪Like a fish stranded on land,
you stay silent♪

616
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:57,940
If tonight I hadn't

617
00:27:57,940 --> 00:27:59,420
gone through those old records

618
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:00,460
and found something new,

619
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:01,300
Wen Zhiqiu,

620
00:28:01,940 --> 00:28:03,540
I'd still be in the dark about you.

621
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,180
You're quite something.

622
00:28:07,380 --> 00:28:09,340
I came here tonight

623
00:28:09,900 --> 00:28:11,180
just to tell you

624
00:28:11,900 --> 00:28:14,180
you're a disgrace.

625
00:28:14,180 --> 00:28:15,060
Absolutely shameless.

626
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,060
Miss Chu,

627
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:19,220
you shared years of work

628
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:20,300
and a relationship.

629
00:28:20,620 --> 00:28:21,620
Even if things fell apart,

630
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:23,500
those words were unnecessarily harsh.

631
00:28:24,020 --> 00:28:25,100
- Exactly.
- Right.

632
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:26,540
Mr. Zhang,

633
00:28:27,180 --> 00:28:29,020
if he had done to you

634
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:30,220
what he did to me,

635
00:28:30,220 --> 00:28:31,940
I doubt you'd stop at harsh words.

636
00:28:32,180 --> 00:28:34,340
You'd probably reach for a knife.

637
00:28:35,420 --> 00:28:36,220
Mr. Wen,

638
00:28:36,500 --> 00:28:37,860
