649
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,940
You'd better watch your back.

650
00:29:05,940 --> 00:29:07,940
I'll never ever forgive you!

651
00:29:08,300 --> 00:29:08,860
She is

652
00:29:08,860 --> 00:29:10,380
a real firecracker.

653
00:29:11,180 --> 00:29:11,780
Zhiqiu,

654
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:13,220
you've really got
to be more careful from now on.

655
00:29:23,500 --> 00:29:25,380
Mr. Wen, all your goods are here.

656
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:26,540
