657
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:27,500
Let me see.

658
00:29:29,820 --> 00:29:30,900
This...

659
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:34,340
Let's check them.

660
00:29:38,020 --> 00:29:39,060
