661
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,020
Once the paperwork is done.

662
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:43,300
When will they arrive
in Hong Kong, China?

663
00:29:45,100 --> 00:29:45,820
Around a week.

664
00:29:47,780 --> 00:29:49,340
This batch of medicine is critical.

665
00:29:49,540 --> 00:29:51,300
