677
00:30:10,660 --> 00:30:11,900
They've all been inspected already.

678
00:30:13,100 --> 00:30:13,740
Ensure everything is checked carefully.

679
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:15,340
Easy, these...

680
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:16,500
Inspect them thoroughly.

681
00:30:17,700 --> 00:30:18,620
