685
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:28,780
Check these out.

686
00:30:30,700 --> 00:30:31,300
See?

687
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:34,380
Look.

688
00:30:35,260 --> 00:30:35,860
There, you see?

689
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:37,620
- That's all.
- Buddy.

690
00:30:38,020 --> 00:30:38,860
These are good.

691
00:30:42,460 --> 00:30:43,420
Look carefully.

692
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:47,620
That's enough.

693
00:30:47,620 --> 00:30:48,380
Don't go too far.

694
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:50,700
No problem with the goods.

695
00:30:51,140 --> 00:30:51,780
Let's check over there.

696
00:30:51,780 --> 00:30:52,340
Let's go.

697
00:30:53,620 --> 00:30:54,180
Come on.

698
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:57,580
Open the box.

699
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:11,220
You filthy coward.

700
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:12,260
After all this time, I...

701
00:31:12,820 --> 00:31:13,300
I...

702
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:14,060
