703
00:31:14,220 --> 00:31:14,980
Who am I?

704
00:31:14,980 --> 00:31:15,500
I...

705
00:31:16,060 --> 00:31:17,060
Who do you think I am?

706
00:31:17,220 --> 00:31:18,700
You crazy woman!

707
00:31:18,700 --> 00:31:19,780
You robbed me of everything,

708
00:31:19,780 --> 00:31:20,780
