709
00:31:21,020 --> 00:31:23,140
I'm taking you down with me!

710
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:23,780
Hey...

711
00:31:25,140 --> 00:31:26,820
He called himself
the heir to a flour mill,

712
00:31:26,820 --> 00:31:28,220
