- Enough!

715
00:31:30,820 --> 00:31:31,900
And clearly, that's not the only one!

716
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:33,180
- Then...
- You crazy woman!

717
00:31:33,180 --> 00:31:34,140
What am I to you?

718
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:34,740
What do I even mean to you?

719
00:31:34,740 --> 00:31:35,820
What are you?

720
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:36,540
What do you think you are?

721
00:31:36,540 --> 00:31:37,380
Why aren't you doing anything?

722
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:38,100
Stop it!

723
00:31:38,100 --> 00:31:38,980
What am I to you?

724
00:31:38,980 --> 00:31:39,660
Tell me!

725
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:40,660
Keep it up and I'll pull the trigger!

726
00:31:40,660 --> 00:31:42,260
