731
00:31:53,620 --> 00:31:54,820
We don't have time for your nonsense.

732
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:55,660
Get lost!

733
00:31:56,300 --> 00:31:57,500
I...

734
00:31:57,500 --> 00:31:58,780
Walk away, or I pull the trigger!

735
00:32:00,300 --> 00:32:01,260
I'm sorry.

736
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:02,620
Sorry about that.

737
00:32:02,740 --> 00:32:03,740
You have no idea

738
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:05,380
what he put me through!

739
00:32:05,980 --> 00:32:07,420
Even if it costs me my life,

740
00:32:07,420 --> 00:32:09,660
I'll make sure he pays!

741
00:32:09,900 --> 00:32:10,780
I'll end him!

742
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:11,380
Go searching!

743
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:13,140
No. We were both swept up that night.

744
00:32:13,140 --> 00:32:13,740
Get lost!

745
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,020
Goodbye, then.

746
00:32:21,300 --> 00:32:21,940
Excuse me,

747
00:32:22,780 --> 00:32:23,740
a bowl of wontons.

748
00:32:23,940 --> 00:32:24,540
Okay.

749
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:45,620
