754
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:07,380
No problem.

755
00:33:08,020 --> 00:33:08,660
Also,

756
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:10,980
we used to work with a trading house

757
00:33:10,980 --> 00:33:12,380
