the procurement to you instead?

760
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:17,980
Yes.

761
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:19,460
Which medicines do you need?

762
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:24,260
The names and quantities
of the medicines

763
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:25,180
are all listed.

764
00:33:32,380 --> 00:33:34,700
Once the medicines arrive in Shanghai,
please repackage them

765
00:33:35,060 --> 00:33:37,300
