regular Chinese patent remedies.

766
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:38,300
Understood.

767
00:33:39,180 --> 00:33:40,300
I'll take my leave.

768
00:33:40,300 --> 00:33:40,820
Okay.

769
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:41,740
Take care.

770
00:34:14,260 --> 00:34:24,780
[Miss Bai Bingxin's Birthday Ball]

771
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:26,340
Thanks, everyone.

772
00:34:28,460 --> 00:34:29,220
Distinguished guests,

773
00:34:29,740 --> 00:34:30,780
