774
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:34,620
Welcome to Miss Bai Bingxin's
Birthday Ball.

775
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:38,420
Let's welcome tonight's guest of honor,

776
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:41,940
the lovely Miss Bai Bingxin,

777
00:34:42,220 --> 00:34:43,500
to the stage.

778
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:56,860
Thank you very much.

779
00:34:57,500 --> 00:34:58,860
Her outfit

780
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:00,420
