at least 100,000 silver dollars.

781
00:35:00,780 --> 00:35:01,300
Yes.

782
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:03,060
And Xia Yuan paid for all of it.

783
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:05,660
Mrs. Xia is truly gracious.

784
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:08,100
