all these years.

785
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:12,300
May the ladies shine ever brighter,

786
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:14,020
and success follow every gentleman.

787
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:14,820
- Great.
- Wonderful.

788
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:19,580
Now,

789
00:35:19,940 --> 00:35:21,060
we're all wondering,

790
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:22,780
