791
00:35:23,540 --> 00:35:26,540
who will Miss Bai share

792
00:35:26,740 --> 00:35:28,580
her first dance with?

793
00:35:28,860 --> 00:35:30,500
To show my gratitude,

794
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:32,820
I'll be auctioning off my first dance,

795
00:35:33,020 --> 00:35:35,860
with all proceeds going to charity!

796
00:35:39,100 --> 00:35:41,780
Miss Bai is gorgeous
and has a heart of gold.

797
00:35:41,900 --> 00:35:43,980
And now, the auction

798
00:35:43,980 --> 00:35:46,020
for Miss Bai Bingxin's first dance
at her birthday ball

