802
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:53,900
Two hundred silver dollars!

803
00:35:54,380 --> 00:35:56,020
Two hundred silver dollars, first call!

804
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,500
Three hundred silver dollars!

805
00:35:57,780 --> 00:35:58,940
I bid 400 silver dollars!

806
00:35:59,460 --> 00:36:00,340
Five hundred silver dollars!

807
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:06,260
