808
00:36:06,540 --> 00:36:08,220
Five hundred silver dollars for a dance?

809
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:09,860
He's truly crazy.

810
00:36:10,980 --> 00:36:12,180
The truth is,

811
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:13,620
he's just head over heels for her.

812
00:36:13,900 --> 00:36:14,980
Five hundred silver dollars.

813
00:36:15,220 --> 00:36:16,660
One thousand silver dollars.

814
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:23,020
Now Mr. Xia bids 1,000 silver dollars.

815
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:25,780
Is there anyone willing to bid higher?

816
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:27,500
One thousand silver dollars,

817
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:28,980
first call.

818
00:36:30,020 --> 00:36:33,180
One thousand silver dollars,
second call.

819
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:35,020
One thousand silver dollars, third...

820
00:36:35,020 --> 00:36:35,900
Three thousand silver dollars.

821
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:36,940
Three thousand?

822
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:40,340
Three thousand silver dollars.

823
00:36:42,820 --> 00:36:43,460
How much?

824
00:36:43,460 --> 00:36:44,500
Three thousand silver dollars.

825
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:47,820
Three thousand silver dollars,
first call.

826
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:52,940
Three thousand silver dollars,
second call.

827
00:36:53,620 --> 00:36:55,860
Three thousand silver dollars,
third call.

828
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,100
I declare

829
00:36:59,780 --> 00:37:02,620
Miss Bai Bingxin's first dance tonight

830
00:37:02,940 --> 00:37:05,300
belongs to this lady.

831
00:37:05,780 --> 00:37:06,540
Miss,

832
00:37:07,020 --> 00:37:09,780
please share a few words.

833
00:37:12,300 --> 00:37:13,860
