834
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:15,340
I hope all the proceeds

835
00:37:15,780 --> 00:37:17,620
will be donated

836
00:37:17,620 --> 00:37:19,340
to the Municipal Infectious Disease Hospital,

837
00:37:19,900 --> 00:37:22,740
to help rebuild the ward that was bombed

838
00:37:22,740 --> 00:37:23,820
by the Japanese.

839
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:25,020
Thank you.

840
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:30,860
Thank you, Miss,

841
00:37:31,580 --> 00:37:33,300
and Miss Bai Bingxin.

